    # oVirt Deployment Options

    The preferred way to install oVirt is by using your operating system's package manager.

    Experienced users can also compile from source, using the guides for the [oVirt Engine](OVirt_Engine_Development_Environment) and [oVirt Node](Node_Building).

    {:.alert.alert-warning}
    If you are new to oVirt and would like an easy way to try oVirt, download our [Live version](OVirt_Live) where you can use oVirt on CentOS without installing it on your machine.


