  ## Install Hosts

  oVirt Engine manages Hosts, and Hosts are where virtual machines run. Now that oVirt Engine is installed, you must install at least
  one Host to have a fully functional environment.

  You can use either oVirt Node, Fedora, or CentOS as Hosts.

  [See the oVirt Quickstart Guide for more information on installing Hosts.](/documentation/quickstart/quickstart-guide#install-hosts)

